ess Cars</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Self-Driving Cars</category><media:content url="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2026/07/02/multimedia/02XP-TESLA-hmgj/02XP-TESLA-hmgj-videoSixteenByNineJumbo1600.jpg" medium="image"><media:credit>Mike Blake/Reuters</media:credit><media:description>A Tesla Model 3 using the Full Self Driving Beta software in 2023.</media:description></media:content></item></channel></rss>